description: Still under Ming’s control Ashley 3000 finds herself under constant servitude to her evil overlord. Tonight she is serving as a cocktail hostess for Ming’s grand Space Party. This is quite a change for an android who was built to pleasure humans and now must enjoy the company of slimy aliens. But she is programmed to do so and in turn, must obey her masters’ commands. Ming shows her off to his guests and lets them know she will be the leader of his Fembots army but first she will entertain everyone with a striptease dance. He instructs her on what to do and humiliates her in every way in front of all the guests. They laugh when she glitches and malfunctions. “Inferior Earth Technology!” Ming yells. When the party is over Ming explains that he must program her with the plans to invade earth. However, he has to use his “Biezel Bop” to do so!
title: Ashley Fires SciFi Dreamgirls Episode: Formal Functions
